                    p GitHub: #[a(target="_blank" href="https://github.com/CDevv/rpgpp") CDevv/rpgpp]
                    p Visit the RPG++ homepage at #[a(target="_blank" href="https://rpgpp.dev/") https://rpgpp.dev/]
                .card
                    img(src="/website/image/index_page/project_logo/nikodex_logo.png", alt="Nikodex logo")
                    h3.highlight Nikodex (for the OneShot Discord Server)
                    p A catalogue of custom Nikosonas that the community have made, based off the game OneShot (this is also the first project where I used Svelte).
                    p GitHub: #[a(target="_blank" href="https://github.com/Niko-Dex/nikodex2-frontend") Niko-Dex/nikodex2-frontend]
                    p Visit the Nikodex at #[a(target="_blank" href="https://nikodex.net") https://nikodex.net]
                .card
                    h3.highlight The Heeler House's website (for the Heeler House Discord Server)
                    p A website dedicated for the Heeler House community on Discord, a community for talking about Bluey.
                    p GitHub: #[a(target="_blank" href="https://github.com/The-Heeler-House/website") The-Heeler-House/website]
                    p Visit the Heeler House at #[a(target="_blank" href="https://heeler.house") https://heeler.house]
